			<h2>
				About the HOPE-NY Community Map
			</h2>
			
			<div id="text">
			<p>
			The HOPE-NY Community Map was created in 2006 in collaboration with Professors Ellen Lukens, Helle Thorning, and Peggy O'Neill. Based on the original design of Professor Susan Witte at the School of Social Work as an interactive learning tool for classroom instruction, the HOPE-NY Community Map offers leaders in the community the ability to develop detailed, interactive maps of resources available to them. 
			</p>

